quoteText:
If you read something that rubs you the wrong way, or if you think of something that should be added, please get in touch! We’re all ears! Email team@roll20.net and we’ll chat.

We don’t amend this document for any particular customer, but if your changes apply to all of our customers, we’ll be happy to update it for everyone.
title: User feedback is invited regarding changes to the terms.
